## Hints for Future Agents
- size_func relies on agent_spans_query computing total_count via a SEPARATE count query
  (clickhouse.py _run_paginated runs count_sql independently of the list limit), so limit=0
  still returns the full match count. If that ever changes, len() breaks.
- get_agent_spans is ungrouped/spans-only by design. Grouped aggregates + stats + custom-attrs
  schema are reachable via client.server.agent_spans_query/agent_spans_stats/
  agent_custom_attrs_schema (PR1 bindings).
- to_pandas works because items are dicts (PaginatedIterator.to_pandas handles dict rows).

